::Koj::
"That's it look like its done." Dorps the torch and looks at the finished 
product.

::Void::
Hovers over the ship "Conducting scans complete all subject matter is locked 
and loaded and battle ready."

::Dark::

shocked a the ship. "A three seater space ship."

::Liono::
Liono Grins as he rotates his sword and puts it away. "Outer space!"

::Key::
"It needs a name its bad luck to fly a ship without a name?"

::Everybody looks at Liono::

::Liono::
"I guess I'm naming it then The Last Dragoon"

::Void::
"It already has a name peel of the tape."

::Liono::
Liono peels of the tape is Golden Crimsom letters: The Lion Assault 2
"I like that better anyway."

::Dark::
"What 3 of us are going? That is one Funky looking Transport."
